iên can)|za|Fouh (diengan)|zh-min-nan|Bō͘ (Thian-kan)|zh-yue|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|lt=Tsuchinoe (戊)|2=ja|3=戊|4=zh|5=戊|zh|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|lt=Tsuchinoe (戊)|2=ja|3=戊|4=zh|5=戊|lt=Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=}}. * The auspicious direction (Eho) associated with Kui is slightly south of due southeast (165 degrees). ==Sexagenary cycles containing Mizunoto (癸)== {{wiktionary|癸}} {| class="wikitable alternance droite" |{{ill|Yin Water Rooster|ja|癸酉|1=Yin Water Rooster|2=ja|3=癸酉|4=zh|5-癸酉|6=ko|7=계유|lt_ko=계유|8=fr|9=Coq de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Hahn|en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|zh|癸酉|1=Yin Water Rooster|2=ja|3=癸酉|4=zh|5-癸酉|6=ko|7=계유|lt_ko=계유|8=fr|9=Coq de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Hahn|en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|ko|계유|fr|Coq de eau|de|Wasser-Hahn|en|Water Rooster|lt=癸酉 (Yin Water Rooster)|lt_ko=癸酉 (계유)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rooster|qq=}} |- style="text-align:left;" |{{ill|Yin Water Goat|ja|1=Yin Water Goat|2=ja|癸未|1=Yin Water Goat|zh|1=Yin Water Goat|2=ja|癸未|1=Yin Water Goat|ko|계미|fr|Chèvre de eau|de|Wasser-Schaf|en|Water Goat|lt=癸未 (Yin Water Goat)|lt_ko=癸未 (계미)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Goat|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Goat|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |- style="text-align:left;" |{{ill|Yin Water Snake|ja|癸巳|zh|癸巳|ko|계사 (간지)|fr|Serpent de eau|de|Wasser-Schlange|en|Water Snake|lt=癸巳 (Yin Water Snake)|lt_ko=癸巳 (계사)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Snake|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} |- style="text-align:left;" |{{ill|Yin Water Rabbit|ja|1=Yin Water Rabbit|2=ja|癸卯|1=Yin Water Rabbit|zh|1=Yin Water Rabbit|2=ja|癸卯|1=Yin Water Rabbit|ko|계묘|fr|Lièvre de eau|de|Wasser-Hase|en|Water Rabbit|lt=癸卯 (Yin Water Rabbit)|lt_ko=癸卯 (계묘)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rabbit|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Rabbit|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |- style="text-align:left;" |{{ill|Yin Water Ox|ja|1=Yin Water Ox|2=ja|癸丑|zh|1=Yin Water Ox|2=ja|癸丑|ko|계축|fr|Buffle de eau|de|Wasser-Büffel|en|Water Ox|lt=癸丑 (Yin Water Ox)|lt_ko=癸丑 (계축)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Ox|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |- style="text-align:left;" |{{ill|Yin Water Pig|ja|1=Yin Water Pig|2=ja|癸亥|zh|1=Yin Water Pig|2=ja|癸亥|ko|계해|fr|Cochon de eau|de|Wasser-Schwein|en|Water Pig|lt=癸亥 (Yin Water Pig)|lt_ko=癸亥 (계해)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Pig|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |}
